caption.text:
Today.. Operations management is mostly talked about planning, organizing and supervising in the contexts of production or manufacturing. 
It is tell how a company do their process in produce a product , it can be measured by a sucessful way during inputs to outputs in an efficient ways.
 The inputs can be worker, resources, materials, machines and so on.

There is big terms that can help answer the question of what is operations management ?  That is supply chain management. Operations management is done through a supply chain management. 
One of important thing is about customized, where it will relevant with manufacture lead time which is a combination of processing time and set time that must be balanced and arranged well to create a good efficiency of time in producing a product.
